PrecisSCHEDULE No. 866 to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS - which establishes a maximum residue limit (MRL) on the amount of the insecticide "TEFLUTHRIN" that can be detected in milk, it being a new soil insecticide used for the control of rootworm and black cutworm.
